data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Step into luxury and comfort in this three-bedroom, two-bathroom single-family home in Davenport's coveted Citrus Isle. The open kitchen concept welcomes you with sleek white cabinets, a solid countertop, and stainless steel appliances, creating a stylish and functional culinary space. The ceramic tile throughout the living spaces adds a touch of sophistication, while plush carpeting in the bedrooms ensures maximum comfort.    Imagine entertaining in your spacious living area or enjoying family dinners in this modern, well-appointed kitchen. The home's thoughtful design extends outdoors with a screened and covered patio, offering the perfect setting for relaxation or gatherings.    The convenience doesn't stop there – your yard is effortlessly maintained by an irrigation system, allowing you to enjoy the lush greenery without the hassle. Privacy is guaranteed with a fenced backyard, creating a secure oasis for you and your loved ones.      Citrus Isle provides a vibrant community atmosphere, complete with a pool for refreshing swims on sunny days, sports fields for active play, and a playground for the little ones. There's always something to do right in your own backyard.    Located in a family-friendly neighborhood, this home offers consumer-validated features that cater to every family's needs. Enjoy the luxury of a short 3-mile commute to school, ensuring that education is always within reach. Plus, with shopping, dining, and entertainment options less than 5 miles away, you'll have everything you need just around the corner.    Embrace the lifestyle you deserve at Citrus Isle – where quality living meets affordability. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this delightful home yours!
